<h1 style="text-align: center;">My tasks and agenda</h1>
<ul>
  <li>Introduction:</li>
  <ul>
    <li>An overview of what I am expected to do as user.</li>
    <li>Can be presented in 2 ways:</li>
    <ul>
      <li>As agenda:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Classic agenda sorted per days and hours.<br/>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <li>As worklist:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>A list of tasks sorted by relative priorities and by patient.<br/>
        </li>
        <li>Task definition:</li>
        <ul>
          <li>.....<br/>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <li>Possibility of several sublists for different types of tasks.<br/>
        </li>
        <li>Some examples:</li>
        <ul>
          <li>In a department of a lab the current list of samples waiting to be processed.</li>
          <li>For a nurse the current list of patient needing a specific procedure.</li>
          <li>For a senior doctor the current list of reports or discharges letters 
          to be reviewed and validated.</li>
          <li>....<br/>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
  </ul>
</ul>
